### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories

### Get category by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/{{categoryId}}

### Create new category
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Category 1",
  "description": "Description for Category 1"
}

### Update category
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Category 1",
  "description": "Updated description for Category 1"
}

### Delete category
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/{{categoryId}}
